---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About Us | ScorpionFix Qatar">
  <!-- Page Banner -->
  <section class="bg-gray-100 pt-[100px] pb-12 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <nav class="flex text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol class="inline-flex items-center space-x-1 md:space-x-3">
          <li class="inline-flex items-center">
            <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 mx-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">About Us</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-dark">About us</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up">
          <h6 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center text-dark">
            Know who are we
            <img src="/img/group-1.png" alt="Procedure Icon" class="ml-2 w-5 h-5">
          </h6>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-dark mb-6">Legacy of Trust and Excellence</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Since keeping your gadgets running smoothly in today's fast-paced world is imperative, Scorpionfix specializes in exceptional laptop, MacBook, gaming, and other tech repairs for Qatar and Doha. We're dedicated to quick, reliable, and affordable solutions because we understand that you rely on your technology every day. We're proud to be your trustworthy partner for all your tech needs.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Scorpionfix started with a basic concept: to close the distance between individuals and professional technical solutions. From modest origins as a service shop in Dubai, then we grew and developed into the most reliable brands for gadget repairs in Oman, Qatar and Doha. Along the road, we have reached important benchmarks such as servicing thousands of devices, forming alliances with big names, and building a devoted clientele.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Scorpionfix's journey began in Dubai and Oman, where we started building our expertise in tech repair services. Over the years, we established a reputation for creativity, reliability, and a strong customer-first approach. These core values have guided us as we expanded into Qatar.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
          <img src="/img/about.1.png" alt="About ScorpionFix" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-md">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Values -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-light border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-10">At the heart of Scorpionfix are core values</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Honesty</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We provide open and honest communication with our clients top priority.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Quality</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Our dedication to quality and accuracy supports every repair.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Reliability</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We are your trustworthy partner for all your tech needs every single day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
